'''塞斯·亚当·梅耶斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Seth Adam Meyers'''}}，{{bd|1973年|12月28日}}）<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/seth-meyers/bio/197065 | title = Seth Meyers Biography | publisher = [[電視指南_(雜誌)|TVGuide.com]] | accessdate = May 16, 2013 | archive-date = 2019-11-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191129082002/https://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/seth-meyers/bio/197065/ }}</ref>是一位[[美国|美国]][[演员|演员]]、[[配音員|配音演员]]、[[编剧|编剧]]、[[執行製作人|制作人]]、[[主持人|电视节目主持人]]和[[喜剧演员|喜剧演员]]。他于2001年起加入[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]]喜剧节目《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》，2006年成为首席编剧，并曾担任该节目的新闻讽刺环节“{{link-en|周末新闻播报|Weekend Update}}”的主播。2014年2月起，梅耶斯开始担任全国广播公司[[脱口秀|脱口秀]]节目《[[塞斯·梅耶斯深夜秀|塞斯·梅耶斯深夜秀]]》的主持人。

==早年生活==
梅耶斯于1972年12月28日出生于[[美国|美国]][[伊利诺伊州|伊利诺伊州]][[埃文斯顿_(伊利诺伊州)|埃文斯顿]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://dailynorthwestern.com/2011/10/19/thecurrent/artsentertainment/q-a-with-seth-meyers-northwestern-homecoming-parade-grand-marshal/|title=Q&A with Seth Meyers, Northwestern homecoming parade Grand Marshal|date=2011-10-19|publisher=The Daily Northwestern|accessdate=2014-03-05|archive-date=2014-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222055743/http://dailynorthwestern.com/2011/10/19/thecurrent/artsentertainment/q-a-with-seth-meyers-northwestern-homecoming-parade-grand-marshal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>其母亲希拉里·克莱尔（{{lang|en|Hilary Claire}}）婚前本姓奥尔森（{{lang|en|Olson}}），是一位中学法语教师；梅耶斯的父亲小劳伦斯·梅耶斯（{{lang|en|Laurence Meyers, Jr.}}）则是从事金融业的工作。<ref>{{cite web |last=Prato |first=Alison |url=http://www.nypost.com/pagesixmag/issues/20081214/SNLs+Seth+Meyers+Power+Fun |title=SNL's Seth Meyers: The Power of Fun | New York Post |publisher=NYPOST.com |date=2008-12-14 |accessdate=2013-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081217051353/http://www.nypost.com/pagesixmag/issues/20081214/SNLs%2BSeth%2BMeyers%2BPower%2BFun |archivedate=2008-12-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/boston/access/1946965372.html?FMT=CITE&FMTS=CITE:AI&type=historic&date=Jul+05%2C+1970&author=&pub=Boston+Globe+(1960-1979)&desc=Miss+Hilary+Olson+marries+Mr.+Meyers&pqatl=google | work=Boston Globe | title=Miss Hilary Olson marries Mr. Meyers | date=July 5, 1970}}</ref>梅耶斯的弟弟是演员{{link-en|乔什·梅耶斯|Josh Meyers}}。梅耶斯的外祖父是[[犹太人|犹太人]]，而父亲一支的家族则有[[捷克|捷克]]（梅耶斯祖母）、[[瑞典|瑞典]]、[[英国|英国]]和[[德国|德国]]的多国混血血统。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://americanisraelite.com/archives/26453|title=Jewz in the Newz|publisher=The American Israelite|date=2013-07-17|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131104181946/http://americanisraelite.com/archives/26453|archivedate=2013-11-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ethnicelebs.com/seth-meyers|title=Seth Meyers|publisher=Ethnicelebs|access-date=2014-03-05|archive-date=2020-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201021124518/https://ethnicelebs.com/seth-meyers}}</ref>他曾在数个{{link-en|犹太社区中心|Jewish Community Center}}进行表演，但并不认为自己是犹太人。<ref>{{cite web |author=posted at 10:53 am on Fri, Mar 23, 2012. |url=http://www.alligator.org/news/campus/article_160fedf0-74ae-11e1-82c5-0019bb2963f4.html |title=SNL anchor Seth Meyers drew about 3,100 to O’Connell Center - The Independent Florida Alligator: Campus |publisher=Alligator.org |date=2012-03-23 |accessdate=2013-08-01 |archive-date=2019-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190404113716/https://www.alligator.org/news/campus/article_160fedf0-74ae-11e1-82c5-0019bb2963f4.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Loohauis |first=Jackie |url=http://www.jsonline.com/entertainment/snls-seth-meyers-to-appear-at-jewish-community-center-lk39ove-134915353.html |title='SNL's' Seth Meyers to appear at Jewish Community Center |publisher=Jsonline.com |date=2011-12-02 |accessdate=2013-08-01 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304085102/http://www.jsonline.com/entertainment/snls-seth-meyers-to-appear-at-jewish-community-center-lk39ove-134915353.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://clatl.com/atlanta/jewish-federation-of-greater-atlanta-2012-community-event-feat-seth-meyers/Event?oid=4294721 |title=Jewish Federation of Greater Atlanta 2012 Community Event Feat. Seth Meyers | Cobb Energy Performing Arts Centre | Benefits | Creative Loafing Atlanta |publisher=Clatl.com |date= |accessdate=2013-08-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131103154324/http://clatl.com/atlanta/jewish-federation-of-greater-atlanta-2012-community-event-feat-seth-meyers/Event?oid=4294721 |archivedate=2013-11-03 }}</ref>梅耶斯在[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]][[曼徹斯特_(新罕布什爾州)|曼彻斯特]]及其郊区长大，高中毕业于{{link-en|曼彻斯特西部高中|Manchester High School West}}。随后他被埃文斯顿的[[西北大学_(伊利诺州)|西北大学]]录取，在校期间成为该校[[兄弟會與姊妹會|兄弟会]]{{link-en|Phi Gamma Delta|Phi Gamma Delta}}（{{lang|el|ΦΓΔ}}）的成员。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newhampshire.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/99999999/NEWHAMPSHIRE09/110429426/-1/newhampshire09|title=Seth Meyers|publisher=NewHampshire.com|date=2013-02-22|access-date=2022-06-16|archive-date=2017-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171003042619/http://www.newhampshire.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F99999999%2FNEWHAMPSHIRE09%2F110429426%2F-1%2Fnewhampshire09}}</ref>

==事业==
