在加入《周六夜现场》之前，梅耶斯是西北大学的即兴喜剧社团“Mee-Ow”的成员，这也是他即兴喜剧事业的开端。梅耶斯随后加入了[[芝加哥|芝加哥]]著名即兴喜剧社“{{link-en|iO剧团|IO Theater|ImprovOlympic}}”，与喜剧团体Preponderate一同工作。他还成为了[[阿姆斯特丹|阿姆斯特丹]]英语即兴喜剧团{{link-en|玻姆芝加哥剧院|Boom Chicago}}的成员之一，<ref>Rapkin, Mickey (September 10, 2004), "Going Dutch". ''Entertainment Weekly''. (782/783):18</ref>而他的弟弟乔什·梅耶斯也是该剧团的成员。<ref name="nbc">[http://www.nbc.com/Saturday_Night_Live/bios/Seth_Meyers.shtml Biography] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090206030905/http://www.nbc.com/Saturday_Night_Live/bios/Seth_Meyers.shtml |date=2009-02-06 }} from the [[NBC|NBC]] website</ref>

2004年，梅耶斯与[[約翰·趙|約翰·趙]]共同出演了喜剧电影《{{link-en|See This Movie|See This Movie}}》。随后在2008年，他与[[布蘭登·費雪|布蘭登·費雪]]和[[安妮塔·布瑞姆|安妮塔·布瑞姆]]共同参演了[[3D电影|3D电影]]《[[地心冒險|地心冒險]]》。梅耶斯还在同年电影《{{link-en|愛情無限譜|Nick and Norah's Infinite Playlist}}》中客串出演了一名醉汉。2008年7月，梅耶斯导演了网络节目供应商{{link-en|Crackle|Crackle_(company)}}的网络剧集《{{lang|en|The Line}}》。<ref>{{cite web | title = For anybody that's ever waited in line to see a movie / Star Trek | publisher = Star Trek Phase II | url = http://www.startreknewvoyages.com/forum/index.php?topic=5588.0 | date = July 26, 2008 | accessdate = February 27, 2009 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110621222100/http://www.startreknewvoyages.com/forum/index.php?topic=5588.0 | archivedate = 2011年6月21日 }}</ref>梅耶斯还主持了2008和2009年连续两届[[威比奖|威比奖]]颁奖典礼。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.webbyawards.com/press/press-release.php?id=176|title=SNL'S SETH MEYERS RETURNS TO HOST 13th ANNUAL WEBBY AWARDS ON JUNE 8th IN NYC|publisher=[[威比奖|Webby Awards]]|date=2009-04-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305164622/https://www.webbyawards.com/press/press-release.php?id=176|archivedate=2014-03-05}}</ref>2009年，他还主持了在[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]][[西雅图|西雅图]][[塞弗科体育场|塞弗科体育场]]举办的[[微软|微软]]大会。<ref>{{cite web | title = Seth Meyers to emcee Microsoft Company Meeting at Safeco | publisher = Seattle PI – The Microsoft Blog | url = http://blog.seattlepi.com/microsoft/archives/178261.asp?source=rss | date = September 3, 2009 | accessdate = September 10, 2009 | archive-date = 2012-07-03 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20120703174353/http://blog.seattlepi.com/microsoft/archives/178261.asp?source=rss | dead-url = no }}</ref>2010和2011年，梅耶斯连续两年主持了由[[ESPN|ESPN]]主办的体育奖项{{link-en|年度卓越体育表现奖|ESPY Awards}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvguide.com/News/Seth-Meyers-ESPYs-1023405.aspx|title=Seth Meyers to Host ESPYs Again|publisher=TVGuide.com|accessdate=September 22, 2010|archive-date=2014-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141129185554/http://www.tvguide.com/news/seth-meyers-espys-1023405.aspx}}</ref>2011年4月，他担任了[[白宮記者協會|白宮記者協會]]晚宴的主持，在开场白中开了[[本·拉登|本·拉登]]的玩笑，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0i7V4NSCFxM |title=Obama plays it cool, laughs off Seth Meyers' bin Laden CSPAN joke |publisher=YouTube |date=2011-01-05 |accessdate=2013-08-01 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124200408/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0i7V4NSCFxM }}</ref>而当时他并不知道，美国情报部门在当时已经锁定了本·拉登的藏身处，并已计划于次日由[[海豹突击队|海豹突击队]]发动[[奥萨马·本·拉登之死|突袭]]。2014年，梅耶斯首次主持了当年的[[第66届黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv/emmys-2014-seth-meyers-wasn-award-worthy-host-article-1.1916780|title=Emmys 2014: Seth Meyers wasn’t award-worthy as host|work=New York Daily News|date=2014-08-25|access-date=2014-09-26|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125021311/https://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv/emmys-2014-seth-meyers-wasn-award-worthy-host-article-1.1916780}}</ref>

===周六夜现场===
梅耶斯于2001年加入《周六夜现场》剧组。<ref name="nbc" />2004年，梅耶斯为“周末新闻播报”主播一职试镜，若成功则将与蒂娜·菲合作主播这一节目环节，但最终不敌[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]。<ref>Gary Levin (September 29, 2006), "'SNL' will update its Weekend Update". ''USA Today''</ref>2005年，他升职为编剧总监，<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.celebritynetworth.com/richest-celebrities/richest-comedians/seth-meyers-net-worth/ | title=Seth Meyers Net Worth | accessdate=2014-03-03 | archive-date=2019-11-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129062828/https://www.celebritynetworth.com/richest-celebrities/richest-comedians/seth-meyers-net-worth/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://nypost.com/2014/02/21/seth-meyers-has-a-powerful-guardian-angel/ | title=Seth Meyers has a powerful guardian angel | work=New York Post | date=2014-02-21 | accessdate=2014-03-03 | archive-date=2019-11-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130180156/https://nypost.com/2014/02/21/seth-meyers-has-a-powerful-guardian-angel/ }}</ref>在同年升职成为首席编剧之一，与[[蒂娜·菲|蒂娜·菲]]和安德鲁·斯蒂尔（{{lang|en|Andrew Steele}}）共同就任这一职位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-st-critics-notebook-seth-meyers-late-night-20140225,0,3495343.story|title=Critic's Notebook: Seth Meyers has strong start as 'Late Night' host|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2014-02-25|access-date=2014-03-05|archive-date=2014-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320074858/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-st-critics-notebook-seth-meyers-late-night-20140225,0,3495343.story}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://comedians.about.com/od/comediansmz/fl/Seth-Meyers-Biography.htm|title=Seth Meyers - Biography|work=About.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140305165505/http://comedians.about.com/od/comediansmz/fl/Seth-Meyers-Biography.htm|archivedate=2014-03-05}}</ref>2006年，蒂娜·菲离开节目组，梅耶斯于是开始独自担任2006-2007一季的首席编剧一职，并与波勒搭档主播“周末新闻播报”环节。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.eonline.com/news/article/index.jsp?uuid=b1b31fb1-7238-4341-9348-425c793c0853 |title=Fey, Dratch Give Up Saturday Night |date=July 24, 2006 |accessdate=November 3, 2007 |publisher=''E! Online'', eonline.com }}{{dead link|date=2017年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.tv.com/story/6449.html |title=Seth Meyers will coanchor Weekend Update |date=September 22, 2006 |accessdate=November 3, 2007 |publisher=tv.com) |archive-date=2020-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206191605/http://www.tv.com/news/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>而2008年波勒离开节目组后，梅耶斯开始独自一人担任这一环节主播的职位，直至2013年{{link-en|塞西莉·斯特朗|Cecily Strong}}开始与他搭档主播。2013-2014一季，这一环节由此二人共同主播。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://variety.com/2013/tv/news/snl-cecily-strong-to-co-anchor-weekend-update-with-seth-meyers-1200612687/ | title=SNL: Cecily Strong to Co-Anchor ‘Weekend Update’ With Seth Meyers | work=variety.com | date=2013-09-15 | accessdate=2014-03-03 | archive-date=2020-12-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205130421/https://variety.com/2013/tv/news/snl-cecily-strong-to-co-anchor-weekend-update-with-seth-meyers-1200612687/ }}</ref>而在2009年秋季，梅耶斯还与艾米·波勒搭档主持了两集“周六夜现场周末新闻播报周四版”。<ref>{{cite news|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|url=http://ausiellofiles.ew.com/2009/07/30/amy-poehler-returns-to-snl/|title=Exclusive: Amy Poehler returns to 'SNL' (REALLY?!)|date=July 30, 2009|publisher=''[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]''|accessdate=January 5, 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090801123507/http://ausiellofiles.ew.com/2009/07/30/amy-poehler-returns-to-snl/|archivedate=2009年8月1日}}</ref>

在[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年美国总统选举]]期间，<ref>Scholibo, Corey (January 13, 2008), "Tina Fey". ''Advocate''. (1022):65</ref>梅耶斯为节目撰写了大量讽刺[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]副总统候选人[[莎拉·佩林|莎拉·佩林]]的喜剧小品，而这些小品则一般由与佩林长相酷似的[[蒂娜·菲|蒂娜·菲]]表演。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/2008/10/29/96258775/seth-meyers-prime-time-political-parody|title=Seth Meyers' Prime-Time Political Parody|work=npr|date=2008-10-29|access-date=2014-03-05|archive-date=2020-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201231170842/https://www.npr.org/2008/10/29/96258775/seth-meyers-prime-time-political-parody}}</ref>而蒂娜·菲在一次参加脱口秀节目《[[晚间秀|大卫·莱特曼晚间秀]]》时也证实了此事。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://politicalhumor.about.com/od/sarahpalin/a/palin-jokes.htm|title=Sarah Palin Jokes|work=about.com|access-date=2014-03-05|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109052009/http://politicalhumor.about.com/od/sarahpalin/a/palin-jokes.htm}}</ref>

在《周六夜现场》节目中，梅耶斯曾模仿了多位名人，其中包括[[约翰·克里|约翰·-{zh-cn:克里;zh-hk:克里;zh-tw:凱瑞;}-]]<ref name="nbc" />、[[米高·肯恩|米高·肯恩]]、[[安德森·库珀|安德森·库珀]]、[[Carrot_Top|Carrot Top]]、[[查尔斯王子|查尔斯王子]]、[[瑞安·西克雷斯特|瑞安·西克雷斯特]]、[[西恩·潘|西恩·潘]]<ref name="nbc" />、{{link-en|斯通·菲利普斯|Stone Phillips}}<ref name="nbc" />、[[托比·马奎尔|托比·马奎尔]]、[[培頓·曼寧|培頓·曼寧]]、{{link-en|本·柯蒂斯 (演员)|Ben Curtis (actor)|本·柯蒂斯}}、{{link-en|泰·佩宁顿|Ty Pennington}}、{{link-en|比尔·考赫|Bill Cowher}}、[[布萊恩·威廉姆斯|布萊恩·威廉姆斯]]、{{link-en|妮可莱特·谢里登|Nicollette Sheridan}}、{{link-en|韦德·罗伯森|Wade Robson}}、[[小唐納德·川普|小-{zh-hans:唐纳德·川普;zh-hant:唐納德·川普;zh-cn:唐纳德·特朗普;zh-tw:唐納·川普;zh-hk:當奴·杜林普;zh-mo:當奴·杜林普;}-]]、[[汤姆·克鲁斯|汤姆·克鲁斯]]和[[凯文·费德林|凯文·费德林]]等。

梅耶斯在[[2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工|2007年－2008年美国编剧协会大罢工]]期间对罢工表示支持。他在一次采访中表示，“我们都知道能到到这份工作是多么幸运的一件事。我们要求的并不多。只是这些规则应该做出改变了，因为人们现在看电视的方式已经和以前不一样了。”<ref>Levin, Gary (November 6, 2007), "Late night without Letterman, Leno ...". ''USA TODAY''.</ref>尽管如此，他也表示很遗憾因为罢工错过了[[2008年美国总统选举|2008年美国总统选举]]部分初选阶段。<ref>Levin, Gary (February 20, 2008). "Weekend update: 'SNL' is back in the race". ''USA Today''.</ref><ref>Meyers, Seth (February 29, 2008), "SATURDAY NIGHT LIVE". ''Entertainment Weekly'' (980):40</ref>

2014年2月1日，梅耶斯参加了其个人的最后一期《周六夜现场》。在节目中，塞西莉·斯特朗和他一同主播了“周末新闻播报”环节，而其好友[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]、[[比尔·海德|比尔·海德]]、[[安迪·萨姆伯格|安迪·萨姆伯格]]、[[弗雷德·阿米森|弗雷德·阿米森]]等人出席节目为他送行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tvline.com/2014/02/01/saturday-night-live-seth-meyers-goodbye-poehler-stefon-samberg/|title=Seth Meyers' Saturday Night Live Send-Off: Who Showed Up for His Final Update?|work=TV Line|date=2014-02-01|access-date=2014-03-05|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125021927/https://tvline.com/2014/02/01/saturday-night-live-seth-meyers-goodbye-poehler-stefon-samberg/}}</ref>

===深夜秀===
2013年5月12日，全国广播公司宣布梅耶斯将于2014年接替[[吉米·法伦|吉米·法伦]]成为《{{link-en|深夜秀 (NBC)|Late Night (NBC)|深夜秀}}》新任主持人，以填补法伦离开节目主持《[[今夜秀|今夜秀]]》留下的空缺。随后梅耶斯宣布将邀请[[艾米·波勒|艾米·波勒]]作为自己主持的《深夜秀》首期节目嘉宾。<ref>{{cite news|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/seth-meyers-named-host-of-nbcs-late-night-lorne-michaels-to-executive-produce/|title=Seth Meyers Named Host Of NBC’s 'Late Night', Lorne Michaels To Executive Produce|date=May 12, 2013|publisher=Deadline.com|accessdate=May 12, 2013|archive-date=2014-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140718063735/http://www.deadline.com/2013/05/seth-meyers-named-host-of-nbcs-late-night-lorne-michaels-to-executive-produce/}}</ref>2014年2月10日，梅耶斯又公布了节目驻场乐队“{{lang|en|The 8G Band}}”将由其在《周六夜现场》工作时的同事[[弗雷德·阿米森|弗雷德·阿米森]]担任主唱。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-st-seth-meyers-reveals-fred-armisen-will-lead-his-late-night-band-20140210,0,6564282.story#axzz2tNVqwiBL | title=Seth Meyers reveals Fred Armisen will lead his 'Late Night' band | publisher=Los Angeles Times | date=10 February 2014 | accessdate=15 February 2014 | archive-date=2014-04-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422104430/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/tv/showtracker/la-et-st-seth-meyers-reveals-fred-armisen-will-lead-his-late-night-band-20140210,0,6564282.story#axzz2tNVqwiBL }}</ref>2月24日，梅耶斯主持的《深夜秀》正式首播，艾米·波勒和[[美国副总统|美国副总统]][[乔·拜登|乔·拜登]]参加了首期节目。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/new-host-seth-meyers-lands-late-night-monday | title=NEW HOST SETH MEYERS LANDS AT NBC'S 'LATE NIGHT' | work=[[美联社|AP]] | date=2014-02-24 | accessdate=2014-03-05 | archive-date=2014-03-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140307231724/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/new-host-seth-meyers-lands-late-night-monday }}</ref>

